' Gambas class file

' Description:
' CVISCA.class
' Support for Sony VISCA protocol to control PTZ camera's

' Development Status:
' Working, a few bugs to fix.

' Links:
' http://www.vision.auc.dk/~tbm/Sony/EVID30.pdf
' http://animatlab.lip6.fr/~gouricho/SonyPTZCamEVID31/evidapplication.html
